#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What is Safeguarding?"
msgstr "Apakah itu Melindungi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What should I do during the disclosure of abuse, neglect, or exploitation?"
msgstr "Apakah langkah yang saya perlu ambil jika maklumat tentang penderaan, pengabaian atau eksploitasi didedahkan?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @global.supervisor_name
#.      @global.supervisor_contact.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**During disclosure:**\n"
"\n"
"💚 Provide a safe environment in which the participant can share their story.\n"
"\n"
"👂 Listen carefully to the participant and take notes: what/when/where/who.\n"
"\n"
"❗ Determine if the participant is in immediate danger and what help is available.\n"
"\n"
"💙 Make sure that the participant feels that you believe him/her.\n"
"\n"
"🌷 Let them know they have done the right thing by sharing their story with you.\n"
"\n"
"✨ Be supportive and free of judgement in your responses – avoid blaming at all times!\n"
"\n"
"➡️ Let the participant know that you will share what he/she told you with your supervisor to find a way to support and protect him/her.\n"
"\n"
"📝 Explain what you are going to do next.\n"
"\n"
" ✅ Notify @global.supervisor_name at @global.supervisor_contact."
msgstr ""
"**Semasa pendedahan:**\n"
"\n"
"💚 Menyediakan persekitaran yang selamat supaya peserta dapat berkongsi kisah mereka.\n"
"\n"
"👂 Dengar keterangan peserta dengan teliti dan buat catatan: apa/bila/di mana/siapa.\n"
"\n"
"❗ Ketahui jika peserta berada dalam bahaya atau kecemasan dan bantuan apa yang boleh diberikan.\n"
"\n"
"💙 Pastikan peserta dapat merasakan bahawa mereka mendapat kepercayaan anda.\n"
"\n"
"🌷 Maklumkan kepada mereka bahawa mereka melakukan perkara yang betul dengan berkongsi kisah mereka kepada anda.\n"
"\n"
"✨ Elakkan menyalahkan pada setiap masa - berikan sokongan dan tidak menghakiminya dalam tindak balas anda!\n"
"\n"
"➡️ Maklumkan kepada mereka bahawa anda akan berkongsi apa yang mereka katakan kepada penyelia anda untuk membantu menyokong dan melindunginya.\n"
"\n"
"📝 Jelaskan apa langkah anda seterusnya.\n"
"\n"
" ✅ Maklumkan kepada @global.supervisor_name di @global.supervisor_contact."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What can I do **after** a participant discloses abuse, neglect or exploitation?"
msgstr "Apa yang saya boleh lakukan **setelah** peserta mendedahkan penderaan, pengabaian atau eksploitasi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**After disclosure:**\n"
"\n"
"❌ Avoid engaging with alleged abuser – that may make things worse and make next steps difficult. It could also jeopardise future legal proceedings.\n"
"\n"
"🌷 You are not alone. Get help from your supervisor to agree on next steps."
msgstr ""
"**Selepas pendedahan:**\n"
"\n"
"❌ Elakkan daripada berinteraksi dengan individu yang didakwa sebagai pendera - tindakan ini mungkin akan memburukkan keadaan dan membuat langkah seterusnya sukar untuk dilaksanakan. Ia juga boleh membahayakan prosiding undang-undang pada masa hadapan.\n"
"\n"
"🌷 Anda tidak berseorangan. Dapatkan bantuan daripada penyelia anda untuk bersetuju mengenai langkah seterusnya."

